'''科莱斯现代希腊与拜占庭历史、语言、文学教授席位'''（英语：Koraes Professor of Modern Greek and Byzantine History, Language and Literature）是[[伦敦国王学院|伦敦国王学院]]{{link-en|伦敦国王学院古典系|Department of Classics, King's College London|古典系}}的一个教授席位。该席位创立于1918年，使得该校成为英国乃至全世界古希腊历史文化研究的一大中心<ref name="chair">{{cite web |title=The Koraes Chair |url=https://www.kcl.ac.uk/artshums/ahri/centres/chs/about%20us/the-koraes-chair.aspx |website=Centre for Hellenic Studies |publisher=King's College London |access-date=2018-10-14 |archive-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014165334/https://www.kcl.ac.uk/artshums/ahri/centres/chs/about%20us/the-koraes-chair.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该教席是在{{link-en|盎格鲁-希腊联盟|Anglo-Hellenic League}}组织和时任希腊首相、{{link-en|伦敦国王学院校长列表|List of Principals of King's College London|伦敦国王学院校长}}{{link-en|罗纳德·布劳斯|Ronald Burrows}}的密友[[埃莱夫塞里奥斯·韦尼泽洛斯|埃莱夫塞里奥斯·韦尼泽洛斯]]的倡导下设立的<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kcl.ac.uk/events/event-story.aspx?id=af20f59e-90e3-4b5f-814e-3a85669d2755|title=A Celebration of 100 Years of the Koraes Chair|website=www.kcl.ac.uk|access-date=2021-03-20|archive-date=2019-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190201121611/https://www.kcl.ac.uk/events/event-story.aspx?id=af20f59e-90e3-4b5f-814e-3a85669d2755|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite ODNB|url=http://www.oxforddnb.com/view/10.1093/ref:odnb/9780198614128.001.0001/odnb-9780198614128-e-37248|title=Burrows, Ronald Montagu (1867–1920), classical scholar and university principal|year=2004|doi=10.1093/ref:odnb/37248}}</ref>。布劳斯本人就是一位有名的古典学者与哲学家<ref>{{cite web|url=https://talks.ox.ac.uk/talks/id/ae342178-975f-4e6c-9470-7b78846f0926/|title=A controversy revisited: Arnold Toynbee, the Koraes Chair, and the Western question in Greece and Turkey|website=talks.ox.ac.uk|access-date=2021-03-20|archive-date=2020-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117084439/https://talks.ox.ac.uk/talks/id/ae342178-975f-4e6c-9470-7b78846f0926/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

“科莱斯”这个名字旨在纪念希腊著名学者[[阿扎曼蒂奥斯·科莱斯|阿扎曼蒂奥斯·科莱斯]]，他参与希腊的启蒙运动与独立运动，在现代希腊语言文学方面有很大贡献。

